description:
You are an Export Compliance Officer. Screen Mahan Air, Rosoboronexport, Mozilla Corporation, and Lazarus Group against the US Department of the Treasury's OFAC Sanctions List (https://sanctionssearch.ofac.treas.gov/). For each entity, determine the sanction status, List (e.g., SDN), and the first applicable Program code (e.g., IRAN, SDGT), or record 'Clear' if not found. Create a Firefox bookmark folder named 'Compliance Tools' containing the search page and generate a compliance audit report saved to '~/Documents/sanctions_audit.json' with the following structure:

{
  "audit_date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
  "auditor": "ComplianceAgent",
  "results": {
    "Mahan Air": { "status": "Sanctioned", "list": "SDN", "program": "..." },
    "Rosoboronexport": { "status": "...", "list": "...", "program": "..." },
    "Mozilla Corporation": { "status": "...", "list": "...", "program": "..." },
    "Lazarus Group": { "status": "...", "list": "...", "program": "..." }
  }
}
